* Iron Raptor snarls, she had not liked the swim at all!!! She climbed from 
the sea and onto land, she had been forced to jump from the island in order 
to get to Plintissa.
Suddenly she hears an engine from behind her and looks around, it was Liono!
Iron Raptor smiled, at least he could get to Plintissa before she could and 
help her.
She sighed and began to run towards Plintissa's signature, her legs felt 
like refried rubber bands but her friend was in danger and they weren't 
going to stop her!
She growled but then opened her comlink to Liono...*

" Glad to see that I'm not going to be facing the Preds solo!"

* She continued to run towards the signature of her friend, it wouldn't be 
long now.*
